Dusko

Welcome

DUSKO is an ongoing satirical surrealist comic book series. The world is weird, technology is glitchy, skyscrapers are getting taller, everybody needs gas, and the population is full of delirious delights.

Each character from the story is available in the form of a collectible NFT. With each new installment, the DUSKO-verse will expand and introduce new characters. DUSKO is entirely drawn by hand, so it is unlikely there will be 10,000 character NFTs. There is also no finite target number, DUSKO is pumping gas at its own rate…
